  "title": "How to change the default mail account used for notifications reports",
  "slug": "smtp",
  "categorySlug": "it-onboarding",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How to change the default mail account used for notifications reports</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">The email used to send notifications can be changed in the settings menu</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>A DevOps from Data &amp; More can help you set up a custom email to send out your notification reports.<br><br>We use <a href=\"https://postmarkapp.com/\" rel=\"noopener\">Postmark App</a> as a default mail provider. If you want a custom mail provider or use office 365 you have the following options.<br><br>Go to the menu in the upper right corner and click on Organisation -&gt; Settings.&nbsp;<br><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" style=\"width: 152px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=152&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png\" width=\"152\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=76&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png 76w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=152&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png 152w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=228&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png 228w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=304&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png 304w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=380&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png 380w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png?width=456&amp;name=image-png-Sep-21-2022-09-11-02-01-AM.png 456w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 152px) 100vw, 152px\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"261\" style=\"width: 290px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=290&amp;height=261&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png\" width=\"290\" data-mce-paste=\"true\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=145&amp;height=131&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png 145w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=290&amp;height=261&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png 290w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=435&amp;height=392&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png 435w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=580&amp;height=522&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png 580w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=725&amp;height=653&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png 725w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png?width=870&amp;height=783&amp;name=image-png-Mar-17-2023-07-44-16-5559-AM.png 870w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px\"><br><br><strong><a href=\"https://postmarkapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PostMark App</a><br></strong>Free and the default mail service</p>\n<p><strong><br>Graph (recommend)</strong><br>If you are using office365, you will need an email account&nbsp; valid Exchange Online licence<br>you enter the account name + domain in the settings at set the validation to GRAPH (that's it)&nbsp;<br><br><br><strong>You can use an SMTP-enabled email account with basic auth.<br></strong>For Gmail and Exchange Online use: port 587, username + password. <br>This setting will support TLS.</p>\n<p><br><strong>You can use any valid SMTP service that does not require 2-factor authentication</strong></p>\n<p>This require that your organisation already set up at SMTP serve</p>\n<p>For internal SMTP use port 25 + a relevant username but no password. This setting will not support TLS.<br><br><strong>Send test mail</strong><br>To test the settings, CLICK \"SAVE CHANGES\" BEFORE clicking \"Test email.\"</p>\n<p>For enterprise users, ensure the server can reach the SMTP gateways.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/smtp"
}